                     <interp inst="t18210718-64-off372" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210718-64-off372" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210718-64-victim636" type="victimName">
                           James Martin 
                           Sanderson
                        <interp inst="t18210718-64-victim636" type="surname" value="Sanderson"></interp>
